    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a id="more"></a><br><code>学习R之前，须先安装</code><a href="http://cran.rstudio.com" target="_blank" rel="external">R</a><code>和</code><a href="http://www.rstudio.com/products/rstudio/download/" target="_blank" rel="external">RStudio</a> :-)</p>
<h2 id="对象类型">对象类型</h2>
<hr>
<p>R中有五类最基本的对象类型：<br><code>character</code> :字符型<br><code>numeric</code> :(real numbers) 数值型：实数或小数<br><code>integer</code> :整型<br><code>complex</code> :复数型<br><code>logical</code> :(True/False) 逻辑型</p>
<h2 id="对象Vector">对象Vector</h2>
<hr>
<p>一个vector中只能包含同类型的对象(除了<code>list</code>，它可以包含各种类型的对象)<br>vector（）函数有两个basic arguments，第一个是vector中的对象类型，第二个是vector的长度。<br>numbers在R中被认为是numeric类型，若明确想要integer类型，则在numbers后加上<code>L</code>.</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="input"><span class="prompt">&gt; x &lt;- 1        </span></span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>(<span class="title">x</span>)</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="string">"numeric"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="input"><span class="prompt">&gt; x &lt;- 1L</span></span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>(<span class="title">x</span>)</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="string">"integer"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>c（）函数也可构造向量对象，可以看成<code>concatenate</code>连接或<code>combine</code>组合：</p>
<figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- c(<span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.6</span>) <span class="comment">## numeric</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- c(<span class="literal">TRUE</span>, <span class="literal">FALSE</span>) <span class="comment">## logical</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- c(<span class="literal">T</span>, <span class="literal">F</span>) <span class="comment">## logical</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- c(<span class="string">"a"</span>, <span class="string">"b"</span>, <span class="string">"c"</span>) <span class="comment">## character</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- <span class="number">9</span>:<span class="number">29</span> <span class="comment">## integer</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- c(<span class="number">1</span>+<span class="number">0i</span>, <span class="number">2</span>+<span class="number">4i</span>) <span class="comment">## complex</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用vector（）：</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- <span class="keyword">vector</span>(<span class="string">"numeric"</span>, <span class="built_in">length</span> = <span class="number">10</span>) </div><div class="line">&gt; x</div><div class="line"> [<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>隐式类型转换</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; y &lt;- c(<span class="number">1.7</span>, <span class="string">"a"</span>) <span class="comment">## character</span></div><div class="line">&gt; y &lt;- c(<span class="keyword">TRUE</span>, <span class="number">2</span>) <span class="comment">## numeric</span></div><div class="line">&gt; y &lt;- c(<span class="string">"a"</span>, <span class="keyword">TRUE</span>) <span class="comment">## character</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>显式类型转换</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="input"><span class="prompt">&gt; x &lt;- 0:6</span></span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>(<span class="title">x</span>)</span></div><div class="line"><span class="input"><span class="prompt">[1] "integer"</span></span></div><div class="line">&gt; as.numeric(x)</div><div class="line"><span class="input"><span class="prompt">[1] 0 1 2 3 4 5 6</span></span></div><div class="line">&gt; as.logical(x)</div><div class="line"><span class="input"><span class="prompt">[1] FALSE TRUE TRUE TRUE TRUE TRUE TRUE</span></span></div><div class="line">&gt; as.character(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="string">"1"</span> <span class="string">"2"</span> <span class="string">"3"</span> <span class="string">"4"</span> <span class="string">"5"</span> <span class="string">"6"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Matrices">Matrices</h2>
<hr>
<p>Matrices是一种具有维度属性的vector,维度为integer型，大小为2，分别为矩阵的行数和列数</p>
<figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; m &lt;- matrix(nrow = <span class="number">2</span>, ncol = <span class="number">3</span>) </div><div class="line">&gt; m</div><div class="line"> [,<span class="number">1</span>] [,<span class="number">2</span>] [,<span class="number">3</span>]</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>,] <span class="literal">NA</span> <span class="literal">NA</span> <span class="literal">NA</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">2</span>,] <span class="literal">NA</span> <span class="literal">NA</span> <span class="literal">NA</span></div><div class="line">&gt; dim(m)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line">&gt; attributes(m)</div><div class="line">$dim</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##按列放置填充矩阵</span></div><div class="line">&gt; m &lt;- matrix(<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">6</span>, nrow = <span class="number">2</span>, ncol = <span class="number">3</span>) </div><div class="line">&gt; m</div><div class="line">     [,<span class="number">1</span>] [,<span class="number">2</span>] [,<span class="number">3</span>]</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>,]   <span class="number">1</span>    <span class="number">3</span>    <span class="number">5</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">2</span>,]   <span class="number">2</span>    <span class="number">4</span>    <span class="number">6</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##可以通过给向量加入维度的属性来构造Matrix</span></div><div class="line">&gt; m &lt;- <span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">10</span></div><div class="line">&gt; m</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">3</span> <span class="number">4</span> <span class="number">5</span> <span class="number">6</span> <span class="number">7</span> <span class="number">8</span> <span class="number">9</span> <span class="number">10</span></div><div class="line">&gt; dim(m) &lt;- c(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</div><div class="line">&gt; m</div><div class="line">     [,<span class="number">1</span>] [,<span class="number">2</span>] [,<span class="number">3</span>] [,<span class="number">4</span>] [,<span class="number">5</span>]</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>,]   <span class="number">1</span>    <span class="number">3</span>    <span class="number">5</span>    <span class="number">7</span>    <span class="number">9</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">2</span>,]   <span class="number">2</span>    <span class="number">4</span>    <span class="number">6</span>    <span class="number">8</span>   <span class="number">10</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##matrix转化为vector</span></div><div class="line">&gt; as.vector(m)</div><div class="line"> [<span class="number">1</span>]  <span class="number">1</span>  <span class="number">2</span>  <span class="number">3</span>  <span class="number">4</span>  <span class="number">5</span>  <span class="number">6</span>  <span class="number">7</span>  <span class="number">8</span>  <span class="number">9</span> <span class="number">10</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##也可以通过cbind()和rbind()函数构造Matrix</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- <span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line">&gt; y &lt;- <span class="number">10</span>:<span class="number">12</span></div><div class="line">&gt; cbind(x, y)</div><div class="line">     x  y </div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>,] <span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">10</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">2</span>,] <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">11</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">3</span>,] <span class="number">3</span> <span class="number">12</span></div><div class="line">&gt; rbind(x, y) </div><div class="line">  [,<span class="number">1</span>] [,<span class="number">2</span>] [,<span class="number">3</span>]</div><div class="line">x  <span class="number">1</span>    <span class="number">2</span>     <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line">y  <span class="number">10</span>   <span class="number">11</span>   <span class="number">12</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="List">List</h2>
<hr>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">#list中可以包含各种类型的对象，对象的index用<span class="string">[[ ]]</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- list(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="string">"a"</span>, TRUE, <span class="number">1</span> + <span class="number">4</span>i) </div><div class="line">&gt; x</div><div class="line"><span class="string">[[1]]</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line"><span class="string">[[2]]</span> </div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="string">"a"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="string">[[3]]</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] TRUE</div><div class="line"><span class="string">[[4]]</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">1</span>+<span class="number">4</span>i</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Factors">Factors</h2>
<hr>
<p>因子记录分类属性的数据，使用有标签的factor要优于整型向量，更有描述性</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- factor(c(<span class="string">"yes"</span>, <span class="string">"yes"</span>, <span class="string">"no"</span>, <span class="string">"yes"</span>, <span class="string">"no"</span>)) </div><div class="line">&gt; x</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="literal">yes</span> <span class="literal">yes</span> <span class="literal">no</span> <span class="literal">yes</span> <span class="literal">no</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">Levels</span>: <span class="literal">no</span> <span class="literal">yes</span></div><div class="line">&gt; table(x) </div><div class="line">x</div><div class="line"><span class="literal">no</span> <span class="literal">yes</span> </div><div class="line"> <span class="number">2</span>  <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##去掉分类信息,则x变成integer</span></div><div class="line">&gt; unclass(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">attr(,<span class="string">"levels"</span>)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="string">"no"</span> <span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">##通过levels参数来改变level的顺序，yes变为第一level</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- factor(c(<span class="string">"yes"</span>, <span class="string">"yes"</span>, <span class="string">"no"</span>, <span class="string">"yes"</span>, <span class="string">"no"</span>),</div><div class="line"> levels = c(<span class="string">"yes"</span>, <span class="string">"no"</span>))</div><div class="line">&gt; x</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="literal">yes</span> <span class="literal">yes</span> <span class="literal">no</span> <span class="literal">yes</span> <span class="literal">no</span> </div><div class="line"><span class="attribute">Levels</span>: <span class="literal">yes</span> <span class="literal">no</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="data_frame">data frame</h2>
<hr>
<p>数据框储存表格数据，它可以将几个不同类型但长度相同的向量用data.frame（）函数合并到一个数据框，它的模样就像二维数组。但要注意：合并的几个向量长度必需一致。每一列数据类型可以不同，可以通过<code>data.matrix（）</code>将数据框转换为矩阵。</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- <span class="typedef"><span class="keyword">data</span>.frame<span class="container">(<span class="title">foo</span> = 1:4, <span class="title">bar</span> = <span class="title">c</span>(<span class="type">T</span>, <span class="type">T</span>, <span class="type">F</span>, <span class="type">F</span>)</span>) </span></div><div class="line">&gt; x</div><div class="line">  foo   bar</div><div class="line"><span class="number">1</span>  <span class="number">1</span>   <span class="type">TRUE</span></div><div class="line"><span class="number">2</span>  <span class="number">2</span>   <span class="type">TRUE</span></div><div class="line"><span class="number">3</span>  <span class="number">3</span>   <span class="type">FALSE</span></div><div class="line"><span class="number">4</span>  <span class="number">4</span>   <span class="type">FALSE</span></div><div class="line">&gt; nrow(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">4</span></div><div class="line">&gt; ncol(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">2</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Names">Names</h2>
<hr>
<p>对象也可以有名字</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- 1<span class="value">:<span class="number">3</span></span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="function">names</span>(x)</div><div class="line">NULL</div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="function">names</span>(x) &lt;- <span class="function">c</span>(<span class="string">"foo"</span>, <span class="string">"bar"</span>, <span class="string">"norf"</span>) </div><div class="line">&gt; x</div><div class="line">foo bar norf </div><div class="line"> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="function">names</span>(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="string">"foo"</span> <span class="string">"bar"</span> <span class="string">"norf"</span></div><div class="line">##list也有名字</div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- <span class="function">list</span>(a = <span class="number">1</span>, b = <span class="number">2</span>, c = <span class="number">3</span>) </div><div class="line">&gt; x</div><div class="line"><span class="variable">$a</span></div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line"><span class="variable">$b</span> </div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">2</span></div><div class="line"><span class="variable">$c</span> </div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line">##matrix的名字dimnames</div><div class="line">&gt; m &lt;- <span class="function">matrix</span>(<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">4</span>, nrow = <span class="number">2</span>, ncol = <span class="number">2</span>)</div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="function">dimnames</span>(m) &lt;- <span class="function">list</span>(<span class="function">c</span>(<span class="string">"a"</span>, <span class="string">"b"</span>), <span class="function">c</span>(<span class="string">"c"</span>, <span class="string">"d"</span>)) </div><div class="line">&gt; m</div><div class="line">   c  d </div><div class="line">a  <span class="number">1</span>  <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line">b  <span class="number">2</span>  <span class="number">4</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="特殊值数据">特殊值数据</h2>
<hr>
<p>为确保所有数据都能被正确识别、计算或统计等，R定义了一些特殊值数据：<br><code>NULL</code>：空数据<br><code>NA</code>：表示无数据<br><code>NaN</code>：表示非数字,代表未定义的值，即<code>not a number</code><br>一个<code>NaN</code>的值也是<code>NA</code>，但是反过来不成立<br><code>inf</code>：数字除以0得到的值,无穷大<br>判断数据是否为这些特殊数据<br><code>is.null(x)</code> <code>is.na(x)</code> <code>is.nan(x)</code> <code>is.infinite(x)</code></p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- c(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, NA, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)</div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="keyword">is</span>.na(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">TRUE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="keyword">is</span>.nan(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span></div><div class="line">&gt; x &lt;- c(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, NaN, NA, <span class="number">4</span>)</div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="keyword">is</span>.na(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">TRUE</span> <span class="literal">TRUE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="keyword">is</span>.nan(x)</div><div class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">TRUE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="获取数据类型信息的一些有用函数">获取数据类型信息的一些有用函数</h2>
<hr>
<p>getClass( )函数我们前面已经见过了，它的参数是表示类的字符串。<br>class( )可获取一个数据对象所属的类，它的参数是对象名称。<br>str( )可获取数据对象的结构组成，这很有用。<br>mode( )和storage.mode( )可获取对象的存储模式。<br>typeof( )获取数据的类型或存储模式。<br>？<code>函数名</code>：函数帮助<br>？’<code>operator</code>‘:操作符帮助，如？’：’</p>
