    <title><![CDATA[python-remove()使用注意]]></title>
    <link href="http://felixmonkey.github.io/2014/11/16/python-remove-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F/"/>
    <id>http://felixmonkey.github.io/2014/11/16/python-remove-使用注意/</id>
    <published>2014-11-16T07:49:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-11-16T08:07:24.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a id="more"></a><br>remove( ) 使用注意</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">removeDups</span><span class="params">(L1, L2)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> e1 <span class="keyword">in</span> L1:</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> e1 <span class="keyword">in</span> L2:</div><div class="line">            L1.remove(e1)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">L1 = [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>]</div><div class="line">L2 = [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>]</div><div class="line">removeDups(L1, L2)</div><div class="line">print(L1) </div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#[2, 3, 4]</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#注意不能直接在对L1遍历时对L1进行remove，否则如上所示，需新建一list</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#相当于复制一个list，具体如下所示：</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">removeDupsBetter</span><span class="params">(L1, L2)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    L1Start = L1[:] <span class="comment">#L1Sart为新的list</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> e1 <span class="keyword">in</span> L1Start:</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> e1 <span class="keyword">in</span> L2:</div><div class="line">            L1.remove(e1)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">L1 = [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>]</div><div class="line">L2 = [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>]</div><div class="line">removeDupsBetter(L1, L2)</div><div class="line">print(L1)</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#[3, 4]</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
